import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='speed', kde=True)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind speed across all locations?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    scatter_plot = sns.scatterplot(x='longitude', y='latitude', hue='dir', data=data)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        scatter_plot.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('How does wind direction vary across different locations?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
